SAS share climbs 7 . 55 pct on optimism . Scandinavian Airlines System ( SAS ) share price climbed 7 . 55 percent on Thursday on growing optimism about the airline ' s performance and foreign interest . At 1215 GMT the share stood at 114 crowns , eight crowns up from Wednesday ' s close in turnover of 799 , 000 shares . Dealers attributed the rise to recent buy recommendations from London banks , improved SAS passenger volume figures and growing optimism about the airline ' s future earnings within the Star Alliance with Lufthansa and others . - - Chris Follett , Copenhagen newsroom + 45 - 33969652 
